### School Management — API Gateway smoke requests
### Requires: stack up (gateway :8080), Keycloak, valid JWT for protected routes.
### Do not commit real tokens; set @token locally only.

@gatewayUrl = http://localhost:8080
@token = REPLACE_WITH_JWT

### Gateway health (no JWT)
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/actuator/health
Accept: application/json

### Auth — login (no JWT; adjust body to your deployment)
# POST {{gatewayUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
# Content-Type: application/json
#
# {
#   "email": "admin@example.com",
#   "password": "your-password"
# }

### Users — list (JWT required)
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/api/v1/users?page=0&size=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### Academic — students sample (JWT required)
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/api/v1/students?page=0&size=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### Academic — class homeroom path (JWT required; note /api/v1/academic/classes prefix)
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/api/v1/academic/classes/grade/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### Assessment — class report collection path (JWT required; routed to assessment-service)
# GET {{gatewayUrl}}/api/v1/classes/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/exam-results?academicYear=2025&term=1
# Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
# X-User-Id: 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### Search (JWT required)
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/api/v1/search?q=test
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json
